  "description": "The signifier (*signifiant*) is one half of [Saussure](../../../../../../humanities/domains/general/domains/people/ferdinand-de-saussure.md)'s dyadic model of the [sign](./sign.md). It is the form of the [sign](./sign.md) — the sound-image, the written mark, the gesture — as distinct from the concept it evokes (the [signified](./signified.md)).",
